## Adjective Endings Quick Reference

<paradigm name="adjective-endings" pattern="-ος, -η, -ο">
<title>Standard adjective endings (covers ~80% of adjectives)</title>

### Singular

|      | Masculine | Feminine | Neuter |
|------|-----------|----------|--------|
| Nom  | -ος       | -η       | -ο     |
| Acc  | -ο        | -η       | -ο     |
| Gen  | -ου       | -ης      | -ου    |

### Plural

|      | Masculine | Feminine | Neuter |
|------|-----------|----------|--------|
| Nom  | -οι       | -ες      | -α     |
| Acc  | -ους      | -ες      | -α     |
| Gen  | -ων       | -ων      | -ων    |

</paradigm>

