## Agreement in Action

<examples name="agreement-examples">
<title>Article + Adjective + Noun</title>

### Nominative (subject)
| Greek                     | English          | Gender    |
|---------------------------|------------------|-----------|
| ο καλός φίλος             | the good friend  | masculine |
| η μεγάλη πόλη             | the big city     | feminine  |
| το καινούριο αυτοκίνητο   | the new car      | neuter    |

### Accusative (object)
| Greek                     | English                    | Gender    |
|---------------------------|----------------------------|-----------|
| τον καλό φίλο             | the good friend (object)   | masculine |
| την ωραία θάλασσα         | the beautiful sea          | feminine  |
| το ζεστό καφέ             | the hot coffee             | neuter    |

</examples>

